videos.headline: BYU scores 75-yard TD on first play from scrimmage
videos.description: Taysom Hill unloads the deep ball on BYU's first offensive play and hits Jonah Trinnaman in stride for the 75-yard touchdown to give the Cougars a 7-0 lead over Toledo.

videos.headline: BYU wins on game-winning field goal
videos.description: BYU kicker Rhett Almond hits a 19-yard field goal as time expires to give BYU a wild 55-53 win over Toledo.

videos.headline: BYU tops Toledo as time expires in a wild showdown
videos.description: After Toledo ties the game on a Kareem Hunt's seven-yard rushing TD and drops the ball on the snap going for a two-point conversion, but somehow converts to take the lead, BYU drives down the field and survives 55-53 on a field goal.
